Articles.Content:
After a long time and now that things seem to be settling down, I'm looking to start a new career save with all my favorite mods. Everything is ready to go except for EVAFuel which does not currently work with any versions beyond 1.10.

I've not been following all the latest developments in the KSP modding community, so I wanted to ask here if this mod has been superseded by something I might be unfamiliar with. Or is it just not that popular of a mod, anymore? Anyway, thanks for your time.
